# Report spec

The sections the `report` skill renders. Edit this to change what reports contain — the skill follows this file, so you never touch skill code to reshape a report.

## Sections

{{REPORT_SECTIONS}}

## Defaults

- **Window:** last 7 days (override per run).
- **Format:** single self-contained HTML, inline CSS/JS, no external assets.
- **Tone:** factual and scannable — this is a status snapshot, not a narrative.
